Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Welcome to this unique opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Imagine building your dream home here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.56,0:00:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}This rare lot is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}A generous 25 by 125 feet of potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Perfect for builders and investors alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Severance approved, ready for your vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Picture a stunning modern design emerging.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Contemporary architecture by renowned Contempo Studios.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Over 2,100 square feet of luxury awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Envision your life unfolding in this space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}With a basement, it’s over 2,950 square feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}All architectural drawings are ready for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Visualize hosting friends in your new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Imagine the possibilities of this blank canvas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}This is more than just a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}It’s the start of your new journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.51,0:00:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{{\fad(300,300)}}Thank you for exploring this opportunity!
